WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: Av65qsd4Vp4

NOTE Language: en

00:00:00.675 --> 00:00:07.910
I'm very happy that you all have decided to marry in Sahaja Yoga,

00:00:08.111 --> 00:00:12.847
but there are certain responsibilities which you must have.

00:00:13.048 --> 00:00:15.847
It's not like other marriages - that today you marry,

00:00:16.048 --> 00:00:20.396
tomorrow you divorce, then you do this, do that. Nothing of the kind.

00:00:20.597 --> 00:00:22.817
You are marrying in Sahaja Yoga

00:00:23.018 --> 00:00:26.777
because we want to strengthen Sahaja Yoga.

00:00:26.978 --> 00:00:30.364
You'll have wife, she'll look after you,

00:00:30.565 --> 00:00:33.245
she'll be kind to you, she'll be loving you

00:00:33.446 --> 00:00:35.721
because she is a Sahaja Yogini.

00:00:35.922 --> 00:00:38.594
And you should also be very kind to her.

00:00:38.795 --> 00:00:43.737
Don't try to dominate, don't try to pass her to your ideas.

00:00:43.938 --> 00:00:48.189
See what she wants. You must know how to love your wife,

00:00:48.390 --> 00:00:51.245
otherwise marriages are not possible.

00:00:51.446 --> 00:00:53.626
But once you divorce in Sahaja Yoga

00:00:53.827 --> 00:00:57.261
we will never marry you again - this we have decided now.

00:00:57.462 --> 00:01:01.904
Or in any way, if you desert your wife or leave her

00:01:02.105 --> 00:01:05.729
or do something irresponsible about your marriage,

00:01:05.930 --> 00:01:08.721
 in Sahaja Yoga you have no place.

00:01:08.922 --> 00:01:11.784
So, once for all, now only you decide

00:01:11.985 --> 00:01:16.649
that you are marrying it's a very, very big responsibility.

00:01:16.850 --> 00:01:20.808
We want Sahaja Yoga marriages to be very successful

00:01:21.009 --> 00:01:26.332
and all of you should enjoy a very happy married life.

00:01:26.533 --> 00:01:31.522
No use dominating, no use controlling,

00:01:31.723 --> 00:01:33.705
but enjoying each other's company.

00:01:33.906 --> 00:01:36.364
Because your wife is also Sahaja Yogini,

00:01:36.565 --> 00:01:39.476
you are also Sahaja Yogi. And we don't marry you

00:01:39.677 --> 00:01:41.952
unless and until you are Sahaja Yogis.

00:01:42.153 --> 00:01:45.373
The reason is: we are enlightened people,

00:01:45.574 --> 00:01:50.413
we are of higher awareness. We have our spiritual life.

00:01:50.614 --> 00:01:55.000
We have to show in our lives how you behave

00:01:55.201 --> 00:01:59.984
very much differently from others who are stupid people,

00:02:00.185 --> 00:02:03.865
who go on fighting, spoiling, everything.

00:02:04.066 --> 00:02:08.667
So that you will have nice children, you have to look after your children,

00:02:08.868 --> 00:02:12.730
look after your family, that's your first thing.

00:02:12.931 --> 00:02:15.373
Of course, some of you will be very busy with your work.

00:02:15.574 --> 00:02:20.071
It's all right, but loving the wife,

00:02:20.272 --> 00:02:24.420
looking after her, looking after children is very important.

00:02:24.621 --> 00:02:26.555
Otherwise you should become bachelor,

00:02:26.756 --> 00:02:29.174
you should not marry. But if you are marrying,

00:02:29.375 --> 00:02:33.039
you are taking the responsibility of the wife.

00:02:33.240 --> 00:02:35.039
She is the daughter of somebody

00:02:35.240 --> 00:02:38.602
and the father is giving the daughter to you.

00:02:38.803 --> 00:02:40.650
So, so far

00:02:40.851 --> 00:02:43.825
boys have behaved very well, I must say, in Sahaja Yoga

00:02:44.026 --> 00:02:46.746
and so now you should also have wisdom

00:02:46.947 --> 00:02:49.587
and understanding that you are here

00:02:49.788 --> 00:02:54.579
to produce Sahaja Yogi children, to help in Sahaja Yoga,

00:02:54.780 --> 00:02:57.690
because we have to change the world.

00:02:57.891 --> 00:03:01.896
It's to be emancipated. If you have very lower level

00:03:02.097 --> 00:03:05.658
of understanding of marriage it won't work out.

00:03:05.859 --> 00:03:09.531
So I've to make a very great respect,

00:03:09.732 --> 00:03:13.031
with great respect I have to make a very humble,

00:03:13.232 --> 00:03:17.079
I should say, request to you that - please, please -

00:03:17.280 --> 00:03:21.396
if you are entering into a married life in Sahaja Yoga,

00:03:21.597 --> 00:03:23.936
you have to understand your responsibility,

00:03:24.137 --> 00:03:26.301
it's a very great responsibility.

00:03:26.502 --> 00:03:28.968
It's a responsibility for the whole world,

00:03:29.169 --> 00:03:31.357
because we have to change the whole world.

00:03:31.558 --> 00:03:35.968
And if you behave like other husbands of your country

00:03:36.169 --> 00:03:37.754
or of other countries

00:03:37.955 --> 00:03:40.119
then what's the use of marrying in Sahaja Yoga?

00:03:40.320 --> 00:03:42.944
You can go and have a nice marriage outside.

00:03:43.145 --> 00:03:45.047
But if you are marrying in Sahaja Yoga

00:03:45.248 --> 00:03:49.087
you have to know it's a big battle against evil,

00:03:49.288 --> 00:03:54.690
against injustice and also against all kind of mismanagements.

00:03:54.891 --> 00:03:59.428
We want to make a beautiful world and to make a beautiful world

00:03:59.629 --> 00:04:06.404
we need people who are beautiful, who themselves respect everyone.

00:04:06.605 --> 00:04:10.499
So, I have to make again and again same request to you

00:04:10.700 --> 00:04:17.451
that you be very good, humble and respecting husbands.

00:04:17.652 --> 00:04:21.491
Don't follow others, because I've had funny things

00:04:21.692 --> 00:04:24.483
and I was surprised how could these people

00:04:24.684 --> 00:04:28.769
become like this in marriages in Sahaja Yoga.

00:04:28.970 --> 00:04:31.840
But we found out they were all mad, lunatics,

00:04:32.041 --> 00:04:34.356
and they behaved in a lunatic manner.

00:04:34.557 --> 00:04:38.824
So aggression and all these things are not allowed.

00:04:39.025 --> 00:04:42.247
You are marrying these girls specially

00:04:42.448 --> 00:04:45.826
for the benefit of the whole world.

00:04:46.027 --> 00:04:49.755
Not only yourself, not only your children, your family,

00:04:49.956 --> 00:04:55.477
but the whole world, before the whole world you have to show that

00:04:55.678 --> 00:05:01.461
you are a very sensible, wise and highly evolved person.

00:05:01.662 --> 00:05:05.080
This is not a marriage of a lower type of people.

00:05:05.281 --> 00:05:09.122
So it's a responsibility with you to show that

00:05:09.323 --> 00:05:15.622
you are very matured and that you have that feeling

00:05:15.823 --> 00:05:19.316
of enlightenment within you. And you are enlightened people.

00:05:19.517 --> 00:05:21.911
And you can enlighten the whole world.

00:05:22.112 --> 00:05:25.467
Of course, because the wife is coming from another family,

00:05:25.668 --> 00:05:27.134
another country maybe,

00:05:27.335 --> 00:05:29.951
so there will be little difference of understanding.

00:05:30.152 --> 00:05:34.586
So you make her understand, you have to talk to her,

00:05:34.787 --> 00:05:37.578
you have to tell her, "All right, come along, sit down."

00:05:37.779 --> 00:05:41.499
But no use losing temper and getting angry.

00:05:41.700 --> 00:05:45.293
Whatever explanation you may give for that is not good.

00:05:45.494 --> 00:05:48.499
It's not going to help you. I want to see all of you

00:05:48.700 --> 00:05:51.697
how you show successfully that

00:05:51.898 --> 00:05:54.665
you are very nicely married to your wives.

00:05:54.866 --> 00:05:57.310
But I don't say you spoil them, by no means,

00:05:57.511 --> 00:05:59.889
I've already told them. Don't have to spoil them,

00:06:00.090 --> 00:06:04.921
but let them be also on the good lines of Sahaja Yoga.

00:06:05.122 --> 00:06:10.175
And become good volunteers of Sahaja Yoga.

00:06:10.376 --> 00:06:13.437
They'll be very good mothers and they'll create those children

00:06:13.638 --> 00:06:18.056
which we want now, who will completely change this world.

00:06:18.257 --> 00:06:21.961
So, I hope you agree with Me and if you agree well and good.

00:06:22.162 --> 00:06:27.128
If you don't agree, even now you can leave and you can give up -

00:06:27.329 --> 00:06:30.445
I will not mind at all. But after marriage

00:06:30.646 --> 00:06:34.524
if you try to misbehave or if you try to divorce something,

00:06:34.725 --> 00:06:39.778
you have no place in Sahaja Yoga. We'll not have you here.

00:06:39.979 --> 00:06:43.992
So, are you all accepting it?

00:06:44.193 --> 00:06:49.867
All right? Whosoever is not accepting raise your hand.

00:06:50.756 --> 00:06:52.817
Thank you very much.

00:06:53.018 --> 00:06:56.365
Thank you very much. I'm very happy to know this.

00:06:56.566 --> 00:07:01.198
So, you have to be wiser and you have to explain to your wife,

00:07:01.399 --> 00:07:04.190
"See now, this is this, this is this."

00:07:04.391 --> 00:07:07.857
And let them see that you are intellectually higher,

00:07:08.058 --> 00:07:12.706
not only that, but you are very wise. Spiritually you understand.

00:07:12.907 --> 00:07:16.849
And then they will listen to you. Be kind, be nice,

00:07:17.050 --> 00:07:20.301
they are leaving their parents, they are leaving their families,

00:07:20.502 --> 00:07:22.809
they are leaving their countries also, some of them.

00:07:23.010 --> 00:07:25.714
So be very kind and gentle with them

00:07:25.915 --> 00:07:28.309
and don't get angry for anything at all.

00:07:28.510 --> 00:07:31.182
There's no need to get angry at all.

00:07:31.383 --> 00:07:34.666
All My life I've never been angry.

00:07:34.867 --> 00:07:37.936
So that shows unnecessarily people are angry,

00:07:38.137 --> 00:07:40.269
there's no need. Just keep quiet.

00:07:40.470 --> 00:07:42.269
If you don't like something, keep quiet.

00:07:42.470 --> 00:07:46.459
But don't show your temper or anger.

00:07:46.660 --> 00:07:50.427
You have to show that you're wise, dignified people.

00:07:50.628 --> 00:07:54.144
I've seen some husbands throwing things, shouting,

00:07:54.345 --> 00:07:56.120
doing all kinds of things.

00:07:56.321 --> 00:07:59.120
Then how can the wife have respect for you

00:07:59.321 --> 00:08:01.358
unless and until you are respectable?

00:08:01.559 --> 00:08:05.001
You have to be respectable, you'll be kind to her, nice to her.

00:08:05.202 --> 00:08:07.969
 I'm not saying you spoil them, not at all.

00:08:08.170 --> 00:08:11.739
If you think something is wrong, then let her sit down,

00:08:11.940 --> 00:08:14.056
you sit down and explain to her

00:08:14.257 --> 00:08:17.802
that this won't be good from Sahaja Yoga point of view.

00:08:18.003 --> 00:08:21.691
All right? So I wanted all of you to wait.

00:08:21.892 --> 00:08:24.278
And so all these years you have grown up now,

00:08:24.479 --> 00:08:27.569
you understand what is the purpose of your life.

00:08:27.770 --> 00:08:30.984
Thank you very much. May God bless you!
